00:10:31.810 --> 00:10:34.180 align:middle line:84%
You can have a very high
degree of prosperity

00:10:34.180 --> 00:10:36.280 align:middle line:84%
with a very simple life
and not much money,

00:10:36.280 --> 00:10:38.990 align:middle line:84%
or you can have a high degree of
prosperity with a lot of money.

00:10:38.990 --> 00:10:41.980 align:middle line:84%
But most people, at
every level of income,

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:44.110 align:middle line:84%
don't experience
very much prosperity.

00:10:44.110 --> 00:10:46.510 align:middle line:84%
They experience
stress, and troubles,

00:10:46.510 --> 00:10:49.610 align:middle line:84%
and unfulfilled feelings,
and all kinds of things.

00:10:49.610 --> 00:10:53.540 align:middle line:84%
So it's not that money can
really bring us prosperity.

00:10:53.540 --> 00:10:55.060 align:middle line:90%
It may be a part of that.

00:10:55.060 --> 00:10:58.180 align:middle line:90%
But prosperity is an experience.

00:10:58.180 --> 00:11:03.010 align:middle line:84%
And it comes from being in touch
with our hearts, and our souls,

00:11:03.010 --> 00:11:06.920 align:middle line:84%
and what we truly need,
want, and value in life.

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:11.350 align:middle line:84%
And the more we are fulfilled,
in terms of what we truly

00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:14.630 align:middle line:84%
need and want on all levels,
spiritually, emotionally,

00:11:14.630 --> 00:11:16.300 align:middle line:84%
mentally, and
physically, then the more

00:11:16.300 --> 00:11:19.720 align:middle line:84%
we're in touch with that, the
more prosperity we experience.

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:22.600 align:middle line:84%
So what I said is, prosperity
isn't really external.

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:25.990 align:middle line:84%
It's an internal experience
that comes, basically,

00:11:25.990 --> 00:11:29.560 align:middle line:84%
as a result of having
our needs met, and not

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:30.610 align:middle line:90%
just our physical needs.

00:11:30.610 --> 00:11:31.410 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:11:31.410 --> 00:11:34.180 align:middle line:84%
>> That's why,
materialistically,

00:11:34.180 --> 00:11:36.910 align:middle line:84%
you can have all the money and
possessions in the world and it

00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:38.710 align:middle line:84%
might make you
happy on some level,

00:11:38.710 --> 00:11:41.860 align:middle line:84%
but it won't fulfill the
spiritual or the emotional

00:11:41.860 --> 00:11:43.272 align:middle line:90%
needs that we have.

