00:15:20.070 --> 00:15:21.070 align:middle line:90%
>> You talk about that--

00:15:21.070 --> 00:15:21.260 align:middle line:90%
>> We have a lot--

00:15:21.260 --> 00:15:21.510 align:middle line:90%
>> --a lot.

00:15:21.510 --> 00:15:22.427 align:middle line:90%
>> --of vulnerability.

00:15:22.427 --> 00:15:24.990 align:middle line:84%
And that is one of the
