00:15:24.990 --> 00:15:26.940 align:middle line:90%
in our culture too.

00:15:26.940 --> 00:15:29.250 align:middle line:84%
We're supposed to be very
strong, and together,

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:33.060 align:middle line:84%
and not need
anybody or anything,

00:15:33.060 --> 00:15:34.780 align:middle line:90%
and have all the answers.

00:15:34.780 --> 00:15:37.320 align:middle line:84%
That's how most of
