00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:54.855 align:middle line:90%
How do we balance?

00:15:54.855 --> 00:15:56.076 align:middle line:90%
>> Balance?

00:15:56.076 --> 00:16:00.180 align:middle line:84%
>> How do we hold and own
