00:16:28.880 --> 00:16:34.040 align:middle line:10%
show your feelings, you show
your needs, you can get hurt.

00:16:34.040 --> 00:16:35.030 align:middle line:90%
That's the risk.

00:16:35.030 --> 00:16:36.860 align:middle line:90%
That's the risk of intimacy.

00:16:36.860 --> 00:16:39.320 align:middle line:84%
