intimacy in our lives,

00:16:39.320 --> 00:16:41.320 align:middle line:84%
we have to be willing to
show our vulnerability.

00:16:41.320 --> 00:16:42.170 align:middle line:90%
>> Indeed.

00:16:42.170 --> 00:16:44.900 align:middle line:84%
>> We have to show ourselves to
another person in order to feel

00:16:44.900 --> 00:16:46.370 align:middle line:90%
intimate.

00:16:46.370 --> 00:16:48.560 align:middle line:84%
