we have agreed upon

00:17:29.940 --> 00:17:35.760 align:middle line:84%
to represent our exchange
of creative energy.

00:17:35.760 --> 00:17:40.250 align:middle line:84%
So if you understand that
money is a symbol of energy,

00:17:40.250 --> 00:17:43.150 align:middle line:84%
you begin to understand
how it works in our lives.

