00:17:49.160 --> 00:17:50.630 align:middle line:90%
We're exchanging that now.

00:17:50.630 --> 00:17:52.340 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, what I'm
saying, for example,

00:17:52.340 --> 00:17:54.850 align:middle line:84%
