00:17:59.250 --> 00:18:00.050 align:middle line:90%
>> I see.

00:18:00.050 --> 00:18:01.510 align:middle line:90%
>> --for that creative energy.

00:18:01.510 --> 00:18:02.390 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:18:02.390 --> 00:18:02.660 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

