>> And you buy my book.

00:18:21.060 --> 00:18:21.400 align:middle line:90%
>> I do.

00:18:21.400 --> 00:18:21.740 align:middle line:90%
>> You see, so--

00:18:21.740 --> 00:18:22.540 align:middle line:90%
>> I did.

00:18:22.540 --> 00:18:25.940 align:middle line:84%
>> --we have each done whatever
our creative energy is,

00:18:25.940 --> 00:18:31.658 align:middle line:84%
