00:18:39.560 --> 00:18:41.210 align:middle line:90%
do that anymore.

00:18:41.210 --> 00:18:46.250 align:middle line:84%
So money is simply a symbol of
the creative energy and skill

00:18:46.250 --> 00:18:49.080 align:middle line:84%
