with one another.

00:18:49.080 --> 00:18:51.170 align:middle line:84%
So if you understand
that money is really

00:18:51.170 --> 00:18:53.850 align:middle line:90%
just a symbol of energy--

00:18:53.850 --> 00:18:54.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Of energy.

00:18:54.840 --> 00:18:58.790 align:middle line:84%
>> --then you can see how it
reflects how energy is flowing

00:18:58.790 --> 00:19:01.490 align:middle line:90%
in our lives.

